          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-paul-flynn" title="Mr Paul Flynn">Paul Flynn</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            Does my hon. Friend agree that one of the most serious jobs is work in the legislature, where one is not just in charge of the workplace but in charge of a war, for example? Would it not be a good thing to show our enthusiasm for the Opposition spokesman's suggestion and lead by example and breathalyse Members before they vote in the Division Lobbies?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0416P1_20040114_WH_12'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mrs-laura-moffatt' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
